#: Game.Levels.FinsetMembership.L04_IntroducingSimp
msgid "# Automating membership proofs with §0\n"
"\n"
"The manual proof pattern from the first three levels works, but it is\n"
"tedious: for each §1 layer you must rewrite, choose a branch,\n"
"and close with §2. For §3 this was 5 tactic steps.\n"
"For §4 it would be 99 steps.\n"
"\n"
"## §5 with a lemma list\n"
"\n"
"The tactic §6 can apply a collection of rewrite rules repeatedly\n"
"until no more apply. When you give it the right membership lemmas, it\n"
"automates the entire search:\n"
"\n"
"§7\n"
"\n"
"This tells §8 to use both §9 and §10 as\n"
"simplification rules. It will:\n"
"1. Unfold each §11 layer (via §12).\n"
"2. Resolve the singleton base (via §13).\n"
"3. Close any resulting §14 goals automatically.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Prove that §15 using §16 with the\n"
"two finset membership lemmas.\n"
"\n"
"In this level, §17 is available -- use it!"
msgstr ""

