#: Game.Levels.PascalsTriangle.L05_SymmetryVisible
msgid "# Symmetry Visible\n"
"\n"
"Look at Row 4 of Pascal's triangle:\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"Reading left to right: §1.\n"
"Reading right to left: §2.\n"
"\n"
"The row is **symmetric** — it reads the same in both directions!\n"
"\n"
"## The symmetry identity\n"
"\n"
"This is the concrete face of the abstract identity\n"
"§3, which you proved in the\n"
"Binomial Coefficients world using §4.\n"
"\n"
"For Row 4, the symmetry pairs are:\n"
"- §5 (both endpoints)\n"
"- §6 (inner pair)\n"
"- §7 (middle, paired with itself)\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Prove the inner symmetry pair: §8.\n"
"\n"
"This concretizes §9 with §10:\n"
"§11."
msgstr ""

