"\n"
"Before diving into the general proof, let us verify the formula for one\n"
"more value. This time, verify it for §0: §1.\n"
"\n"
"You can use §2 with the sum-unfolding lemmas, or you can unfold\n"
"manually with §3 repeated three times, followed\n"
"by §4, and then §5.\n"
"\n"
"## Manual unfolding\n"
"\n"
"If you want to see each step:\n"
"1. §6 — peels off the §7 term\n"
"2. §8 — peels off the §9 term\n"
"3. §10 — peels off the §11 term\n"
"4. §12 — the empty sum is §13\n"
