#: Game.Levels.FinCompute.L11_Boss
msgid "# Boss Level: Integrating Everything\n"
"\n"
"Time to combine all the skills from this world.\n"
"\n"
"You will prove a conjunction of two facts:\n"
"\n"
"1. A **numeric computation** with powers: §0\n"
"2. A **universal property** about §1: for every §2, §3\n"
"\n"
"## Why this is an integration challenge\n"
"\n"
"The two conjuncts require **different proof strategies**:\n"
"\n"
"- Part 1 is a concrete numeric equality involving powers. Use §4\n"
"  to evaluate it directly.\n"
"- Part 2 is a universally quantified property about §5 involving powers.\n"
"  You need §6 to enumerate all five elements, then §7 to\n"
"  evaluate each case.\n"
"\n"
"You will need to:\n"
"1. Use §8 to split the conjunction\n"
"2. Solve part 1 with §9\n"
"3. Solve part 2 with §10\n"
"\n"
"There is no new material --- only integration."
msgstr ""

