#: Game.Levels.FinsetOperations.L10_Boss
msgid "# Boss: De Morgan's law for finite sets\n"
"\n"
"Time to integrate everything from this world. You will prove\n"
"**De Morgan's law for finsets**:\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"This says: the elements of §1 that are **not** in §2 are exactly\n"
"those that are not in §3 **or** not in §4.\n"
"\n"
"## Proof plan\n"
"\n"
"1. Use §5 to reduce to membership.\n"
"2. Use §6 to split the biconditional.\n"
"3. **Forward**: From §7, extract §8 and\n"
"   §9. Use the fact that §10 means it is not the\n"
"   case that §11 **and** §12. Use §13 on §14 to\n"
"   determine which side of §15 receives §16.\n"
"4. **Reverse**: From §17, case-split on\n"
"   which part of the union §18 came from, and in each case show\n"
"   §19.\n"
"\n"
"This proof uses every major tool from this world: §20, §21,\n"
"§22, §23, §24, §25, and §26."
