"- \"§44 has distinct components because §45.\" (L03)\n"
"- \"§46 is injective: outputs are distinct.\" (L04)\n"
"- \"Same function is surjective: §47, §48, §49.\" (L05)\n"
"- \"§50 is not surjective: §51 has no preimage.\" (L06)\n"
"- \"§52 is not injective: §53.\" (L07)\n"
"- \"§54 has §55 elements.\" (L08)\n"
"- \"§56 is bijective (a permutation).\" (L09)\n"
"- \"Swapping 1 and 2 twice returns to the original arrangement.\" (L10)\n"
"- \"§57 is bijective (a permutation).\" (L11)\n"
"\n"
