msgid "# Analyzing a membership hypothesis\n"
"\n"
"In every level so far, you have **built** membership proofs from\n"
"scratch -- rewriting the goal, choosing branches, and closing with\n"
"a hypothesis. This is **forward** reasoning: you transform the goal\n"
"until it matches something you know.\n"
"\n"
"But sometimes you start with a membership hypothesis and need to\n"
"**take it apart**. If you know §0, what can you\n"
"conclude? By §1, this means §2.\n"
"\n"
"## Rewriting a hypothesis\n"
"\n"
"You already know §3 rewrites the **goal**. To rewrite\n"
"a **hypothesis** §4 instead, write:\n"
"§5\n"
"\n"
"After §6, the hypothesis §7\n"
"becomes §8.\n"
"\n"
"## Case-splitting with §9\n"
"\n"
"When a hypothesis is a disjunction §10, you can split into\n"
"two cases with:\n"
"§11\n"
"\n"
"This creates two subgoals: one where §12, and one where §13.\n"
"You prove the goal separately in each case.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Prove that membership in an append is symmetric: if §14,\n"
"then §15.\n"
"\n"
"**Strategy**:\n"
"1. §16 to unfold the hypothesis into a disjunction\n"
"2. §17 to split into cases\n"
"3. In each case, §18 on the goal, choose the right\n"
"   branch (§19 or §20), and close with §21"
msgstr ""

