#: Game.Levels.FinIntro.L04_RoundTrip
msgid "# §0 and §1 are inverses\n"
"\n"
"You have learned two operations:\n"
"- §2 constructs a §3 element from a number and a proof\n"
"- §4 extracts the number from a §5 element\n"
"\n"
"These are inverses. If you start with §6, extract its value §7\n"
"and its proof §8, and then reconstruct §9, you\n"
"get §10 back.\n"
"\n"
"This round-trip identity says: a §11 element is *nothing more* than a\n"
"natural number with a proof of boundedness. There is no hidden data -- you\n"
"can always take it apart and put it back together.\n"
"\n"
