"\n"
"## The counterexample: §9\n"
"\n"
"Neither of these statements can even be *stated* for §10, because\n"
"§11 does not exist. The §12 instance is\n"
"a prerequisite, and §13 does not have one.\n"
"\n"
"This is how Lean enforces finiteness: not by runtime checks, but by\n"
