msgid "# §0 with Structured Goals\n"
"\n"
"So far, you have used §1 where each case was\n"
"a single goal. Now let's combine §2 with §3 to\n"
"handle conjunctions --- goals that have two parts.\n"
"\n"
"## The pattern\n"
"\n"
"When each case of §4 produces a conjunction, you need to\n"
"split each case with §5 before closing. The combination\n"
