#: Game.Levels.ListBasics.L02_ListLength
msgid "# Reasoning about §0\n"
"\n"
"Every list has a **length** -- the number of elements it contains.\n"
"The function §1 computes this recursively:\n"
"\n"
"- §2 (the empty list has no elements)\n"
"- §3 (consing adds one to the length)\n"
"\n"
"In this level, you will not just evaluate length on a concrete list.\n"
"Instead, you will prove a **symbolic** fact: given any list §4 of\n"
"natural numbers, §5.\n"
"\n"
"## The key lemma\n"
"\n"
"The fact you need is §6:\n"
"§7\n"
"\n"
"This is how §8 unfolds on a cons cell.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Use §9 to rewrite the left-hand side."
msgstr ""

