"\n"
"In Lean, this is the lemma §2:\n"
"\n"
"§3\n"
"\n"
"This says: a sum of pointwise sums splits into a sum of each part.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Prove:\n"
"§4\n"
"\n"
"Use §5."
msgstr ""

