msgid "# Boss: Squaring an Upper-Triangular Matrix\n"
"\n"
"Time to integrate everything from this world. You will prove two facts\n"
"about the upper-triangular matrix:\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"**Part 1**: §1\n"
"\n"
"**Part 2**: §2\n"
"\n"
"## Strategy for Part 1\n"
"\n"
"To prove matrix equality, use §3 to reduce to entry-wise\n"
"equality. Then for each entry:\n"
"\n"
"1. §4 — expand the product\n"
"2. §5 — unfold the sum\n"
"3. §6 — evaluate the arithmetic\n"
