"\n"
"Time to integrate everything. You will prove a concrete sum identity\n"
"by combining §0, §1, §2, and arithmetic.\n"
"\n"
"## The statement\n"
"\n"
"Prove that the sum of §3 over the union of §4 and §5\n"
"equals §6.\n"
"\n"
"## Strategy\n"
"\n"
"1. Use §7 to split the sum over the disjoint union.\n"
"2. Use §8 on §9 to peel off §10.\n"
