#: Game.Levels.CountingPigeonhole.L02_FunctionCardinality
msgid "The exponential counting principle:\n"
"\n"
"1. §0 gave: §1.\n"
"2. §2 evaluated: §3.\n"
"3. §4 computed: §5.\n"
"\n"
"## The multiplication principle for functions\n"
"\n"
"Why §6? Each of the 2 inputs independently chooses from 3 outputs.\n"
"By the multiplication principle, the total count is §7.\n"
"\n"
"More generally, §8. This is\n"
"the exponential rule for counting functions, and it is why function\n"
"types are sometimes written with exponential notation.\n"
"\n"
"**In plain language**: \"There are §9 ways to assign one of three\n"
"values to each of two slots.\""
msgstr ""

#. §0: `Finset.card_le_card`
