#: Game.Levels.Capstone.L05_PowersetBinomial
msgid "# Powerset cardinality = sum of binomial coefficients\n"
"\n"
"One of the most elegant connections in combinatorics: the number of\n"
"subsets of an §0-element set equals §1, which also equals the sum\n"
"of all binomial coefficients §2.\n"
"\n"
"## The two sides\n"
"\n"
"**Left side** (from the **FinsetCardinality** world):\n"
"§3\n"
"\n"
"**Right side** (from the **BinomialCoefficients** / **BinomialTheorem** worlds):\n"
"§4\n"
"\n"
"Since both sides equal §5, they are equal to each other.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Prove that §6.\n"
"\n"
"This connects the **finset** module with the **binomial coefficient** module."
msgstr ""

