"   and finds a match.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof moves used**:\n"
"- §6 to split the conjunction\n"
"- §7 for definitional equality (length computation)\n"
"- §8 for decidable proposition (membership check)\n"
"\n"
"**In plain language**: \"The sequence 1, 2, 1, 3 has four entries. The\n"
"number 2 appears among them.\"\n"
"\n"
