msgid "# Applying a function to every element\n"
"\n"
"§0 applies the function §1 to every element of §2, producing\n"
"a new list of the same length.\n"
"\n"
"For example:\n"
"- §3\n"
"- §4\n"
"\n"
"## Map preserves membership\n"
"\n"
"If §5 is in §6, then §7 is in §8. This is the key\n"
"property that connects list membership before and after mapping.\n"
"\n"
"The lemma you need is §9:\n"
"§10\n"
"\n"
"This says: §11 is in the mapped list if and only if there exists some\n"
"element §12 in the original list such that §13.\n"
"\n"
"(Note: §14 is notation for §15.)\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
