"\n"
"## The disjointness requirement\n"
"\n"
"§0 only works when §1 and §2 are disjoint. If they overlap,\n"
"an element in §3 would be counted once in §4\n"
"but appears in both §5 and §6, so the\n"
"equation would fail.\n"
"\n"
"## Comparison with cardinality\n"
"\n"
