"- §8 says §9\n"
"- §10 says §11\n"
"\n"
"**In plain language**: \"When two sets don't overlap, the total sum\n"
"splits into the sum over each part. This is the additive analogue of\n"
"the cardinality formula for disjoint unions.\""
