#: Game.Levels.BinomialCoefficients.L07_CountingSubsets
msgid "# Counting Subsets: The Combinatorial Interpretation\n"
"\n"
"The binomial coefficient §0 counts the number of\n"
"§1-element subsets of an §2-element set. In Lean, this is made\n"
"precise using §3 and §4:\n"
"\n"
"The number of §5-element subsets of §6 is exactly §7.\n"
