"of ways to choose §2 elements from a set of §3 elements. It appears\n"
"throughout combinatorics, algebra, and probability.\n"
"\n"
"## Definition\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, the binomial coefficient is §4. It is defined\n"
"recursively using Pascal's rule:\n"
"\n"
"§5\n"
"\n"
