"\n"
"You proved §0 from first principles — no library lemma,\n"
"just the recursive definition.\n"
"\n"
"## The proof structure\n"
"\n"
"- **Base**: §1 by §2\n"
"- **Step**: §3\n"
"\n"
"Each rewrite step used a single lemma:\n"
"1. §4 — applied Pascal's rule with §5\n"
"2. §6 — simplified §7\n"
"3. §8 — applied the inductive hypothesis\n"
"4. §9 — rearranged §10\n"
"\n"
"## What you learned in this world\n"
"\n"
"- **L01**: §11 definition and recursive computation\n"
"- **L02**: Boundary values: §12, §13, §14\n"
"- **L03**: §15 when §16 (C10 misconception)\n"
"- **L04**: Pascal's rule: §17\n"
"- **L05**: Pascal's rule applied to compute specific values\n"
"- **L06**: Symmetry: §18\n"
"- **L07**: Combinatorial interpretation: §19\n"
"- **L08**: Row sum: §20\n"
"- **L09**: Boss — §21 by induction\n"
"\n"
"## Transfer moment\n"
"\n"
