"## The method\n"
"\n"
"Given a target identity involving §2, ask: *\"Is there a\n"
"substitution of §3 and §4 that produces this?\"*\n"
"\n"
"| Substitution | Identity |\n"
"|-------------|---------|\n"
"| §5 | §6 (row sum) |\n"
"| §7 | §8 (alternating sum) |\n"
"| §9 | §10 (Level 4) |\n"
"| §11 | §12 (Boss of W19) |\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Prove the alternating sum identity for a specific §13. This retrieves\n"
"the alternating sum lemma on a fresh surface form."
