#: Game.Levels.RangeSumInduction.L03_FirstInductiveSum
msgid "Congratulations on your first inductive sum proof!\n"
"\n"
"## The three-step pattern\n"
"\n"
"Every inductive proof on range sums follows this template:\n"
"\n"
"1. **§0** — split into base case and inductive step.\n"
"2. **Base case**: §1 (or §2), since the\n"
"   sum over an empty range is §3.\n"
"3. **Inductive step**: §4, then close the\n"
"   arithmetic.\n"
"\n"
"In this level the arithmetic was trivial (both sides became §5\n"
"after rewriting). In harder levels, you will need §6 or §7 to\n"
"close the final equality."
msgstr ""

