#. §7: `a ∈ l₁ ++ l₂ ↔ a ∈ l₁ ∨ a ∈ l₂`
#. §8: `(l₁ ++ l₂) ++ l₃ = l₁ ++ (l₂ ++ l₃)`
#: Game.Levels.ListBasics.L04_MemAppend
msgid "You proved that membership in the first list implies membership in the\n"
"concatenation. The proof unfolded §0 into §1,\n"
"chose the left side, and used the hypothesis.\n"
"\n"
"Notice the similarity to the previous level: once you unfold the\n"
"membership condition, the structure of the proof is about §2 -- choosing\n"
"which disjunct to verify. This is a recurring pattern in list proofs.\n"
"\n"
"The symmetric fact also holds: if §3, then §4 (choosing\n"
"the right disjunct instead). Together, these give the full §5.\n"
"\n"
"**Key properties of append**:\n"
