#: Game.Levels.FinsetProd.L04_RingForProducts
msgid "# Algebraic manipulation with §0\n"
"\n"
"You have used §1 in earlier worlds to close arithmetic equalities.\n"
"In this level you will combine §2 with §3 to prove\n"
"a product identity by induction.\n"
"\n"
"## The statement\n"
"\n"
"Prove by induction:\n"
"§4\n"
"\n"
"In Lean: §5.\n"
"\n"
"## Strategy\n"
"\n"
"1. §6\n"
"2. Base case: §7, so the product is §8. And §9.\n"
"   Use §10.\n"
"3. Inductive step:\n"
"   - §11 — peel off the last §12 and\n"
"     apply the hypothesis.\n"
"   - §13 closes §14."
msgstr ""

