#: Game.Levels.BigOpAdvanced.L07_BasicReindex
msgid "You completed your first reindexing proof using §0!\n"
"\n"
"## The five obligations\n"
"\n"
"When you use §1 with a forward map §2 and inverse §3, you\n"
"prove:\n"
"1. **Forward maps into target**: §4 sends §5 into §6\n"
"2. **Inverse maps into source**: §7 sends §8 into §9\n"
"3. **Left inverse**: §10 for §11\n"
"4. **Right inverse**: §12 for §13\n"
"5. **Function values match**: §14 for §15\n"
"\n"
"These correspond exactly to the conditions for a change of variables\n"
"in a sum.\n"
"\n"
"## Practical tips\n"
"\n"
"- The membership obligations often reduce to arithmetic; §16 is\n"
"  your friend.\n"
"- The inverse obligations are usually immediate from the definitions.\n"
"- The function-value obligation is often §17 or §18.\n"
"\n"
"## What comes next\n"
"\n"
"The next level practices reindexing with a slightly more involved\n"
"example."
msgstr ""

