#: Game.Levels.MultisetHierarchy.L08_ToFinset
msgid "The conversion §0 removes duplicates: the multiset\n"
"§1 had two copies of §2, but the finset §3\n"
"contains each element at most once.\n"
"\n"
"This is the second step in the hierarchy:\n"
"1. §4: forget **order** (via §5)\n"
"2. §6: forget **multiplicity** (via §7)\n"
"\n"
"Notice that information is lost at each step:\n"
"- After step 1, you can no longer tell whether §8 came before or after §9\n"
"- After step 2, you can no longer tell that §10 appeared twice\n"
"\n"
"**In plain language**: \"Converting a bag to a set means keeping only the\n"
"distinct items and forgetting how many copies of each you had.\""
msgstr ""

