"\n"
"§1\n"
"\n"
"It rewrites §2 to §3. So\n"
"§4 with §5 gives §6,\n"
"i.e., §7.\n"
"\n"
"That is the *reverse* of our goal. Use §8 first to flip the\n"
"goal to §9.\n"
"\n"
"Try §10."
msgstr ""

