#: Game.Levels.FinsetConstructors.L04_NotationDesugaring
msgid "# How §0 really works\n"
"\n"
"In the last level, you saw that §1 desugars to §2. Now\n"
"let us see the full picture with three elements.\n"
"\n"
"## The desugaring chain\n"
"\n"
"§3\n"
"\n"
"Reading right-to-left:\n"
"1. Start with §4\n"
"2. Insert §5 to get §6\n"
"3. Insert §7 to get §8\n"
"4. Insert §9 to get §10\n"
"\n"
"The outermost element in the notation is the **first** §11.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Prove that §12 equals §13 as a finset.\n"
"\n"
"This exercises the notation desugaring: you need to see that both sides\n"
"are the same expression."
msgstr ""

