#: Game.Levels.ThreeFiniteness.L04_Converting
msgid "# From §0 to §1\n"
"\n"
"You have seen how to go *from* §2 or §3 *to* §4.\n"
"Now you will go the other direction: from a §5 proof to a\n"
"§6.\n"
"\n"
"## §7\n"
"\n"
"Given a proof §8, the term §9 is a §10\n"
"whose elements are exactly the elements of §11:\n"
"\n"
"§12\n"
"\n"
"The membership characterization is:\n"
"\n"
"§13\n"
"\n"
"So §14 is a finset that represents the same collection as the\n"
"set §15, but as concrete data rather than a predicate.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Given a proof §16 that §17 is finite, prove that §18\n"
"belongs to §19.\n"
"\n"
"Strategy: rewrite with §20 to translate the finset\n"
"membership into set membership, then prove §21."
