#: Game.Levels.FinsetTransformations.L04_ImageWitness
msgid "# Finding the right witness\n"
"\n"
"In the last level, the witness was obvious: §0 doubles to §1.\n"
"This time the function is less transparent, so you will need to\n"
"think about which element maps to the target.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Consider the function §2 applied to {0, 1, 2, 3}.\n"
"Prove that §3 belongs to the image.\n"
"\n"
"You need to find §4 with §5. Since\n"
"§6, the witness is §7.\n"
"\n"
"## Reminder\n"
"\n"
"The proof shape is:\n"
"1. §8 to expose the existential.\n"
"2. §9 to provide the witness.\n"
"3. Prove §10 and §11."
