#: Game.Levels.FinCompute.L01_FinCases
msgid "# Exhaustive Case Analysis on §0\n"
"\n"
"In the previous world, you proved properties of §1 elements using\n"
"§2 and §3. But there is a much more direct approach for *small*\n"
"§4: simply check every possible value.\n"
"\n"
"## The §5 tactic\n"
"\n"
"When you have a hypothesis §6 (for a concrete §7), the tactic\n"
"§8 replaces the single goal with §9 separate goals --- one\n"
"for each possible value of §10.\n"
"\n"
"For example, if §11, then §12 produces three goals\n"
"where §13 is replaced by §14, §15, and §16 respectively.\n"
"\n"
"This is the **exhaustive verification** pattern: you verify the claim for\n"
"every element individually, and since §17 has exactly §18 elements,\n"
"that covers everything.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Prove that every element of §19 satisfies §20.\n"
"\n"
"After §21 and §22, you will have three goals.\n"
"Each one is a concrete arithmetic statement that §23 can handle.\n"
"You can close each goal separately with §24, or handle all three\n"
"at once --- we will learn how in the next level."
