"\n"
"1. **Rewrite** with §0 to expose the disjunction.\n"
"2. **Choose a branch** with §1 (since §2 is in the first finset).\n"
"3. **Close** the membership with §3.\n"
"\n"
"The key insight: membership in §4 reduces to membership in §5 **or**\n"
"membership in §6. This is the finset version of the familiar set-theory\n"
"fact.\n"
"\n"
"**In plain language**: \"2 is in {1, 2, 3} ∪ {3, 4, 5} because 2 is in\n"
