#: Game.Levels.MultisetHierarchy.L07_CountSymbolic
msgid "# Reasoning about count with rewriting\n"
"\n"
"In Level 6, you proved §0 by §1.\n"
"That worked because the multiset was concrete. But what if you need to\n"
"reason about counting in a more general way?\n"
"\n"
"## The recursive structure of count\n"
"\n"
"Counting in a multiset built by §2 follows two rules:\n"
"\n"
"### §3\n"
"§4\n"
"When you add §5 to a multiset and then count §6, the count increases by 1.\n"
"\n"
"### §7\n"
"§8\n"
"When you add a **different** element §9 and count §10, the count does not change.\n"
"\n"
"Here §11 is multiset cons: §12 adds element §13 to multiset §14.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
