"§3 must be §4, so §5.\n"
"\n"
"Let's contrast the boundary cases:\n"
"- §6 has **0 elements** (empty type)\n"
"- §7 has **1 element** (the number §8)\n"
"- §9 has **2 elements** (§10 and §11)\n"
"- §12 has **n elements** (§13)\n"
