#: Game.Levels.FinsetConstructors.L02_Singletons
msgid "# Building a finset with one element\n"
"\n"
"The next step up from the empty finset is a finset with exactly one element:\n"
"a **singleton**. When you write §0 in a finset context, Lean builds a\n"
"finset containing only the element §1.\n"
"\n"
"## How singletons are built\n"
"\n"
"Under the hood, §2 is the same as §3 -- start with the empty\n"
"finset and insert one element. (You will learn about §4 in the\n"
"next level.)\n"
"\n"
"## Cardinality\n"
"\n"
