"\n"
"## The pattern\n"
"\n"
"To prove §2 for matrices over §3:\n"
"\n"
"1. §4 — reduce to entry-wise equality\n"
"2. §5 — enumerate all index pairs\n"
"3. Close each case by computation (§6, §7, etc.)\n"
"\n"
"This pattern works because §8 is finite and Lean can enumerate\n"
"its elements.\n"
"\n"
