#: Game.Levels.MultisetHierarchy.L02_MultisetMem
msgid "# Membership in a multiset\n"
"\n"
"Membership is the most fundamental operation on any collection type.\n"
"You saw §0 (written §1) in the Lists world. Multisets\n"
"have an analogous notion: §2 for §3.\n"
"\n"
"## The bridge lemma: §4\n"
"\n"
"When you coerce a list to a multiset, membership is preserved:\n"
"\n"
"§5\n"
