#: Game.Levels.CountingPset.L07_Boss
msgid "# Boss: Multi-step counting argument\n"
"\n"
"Combine everything from this problem set into a single proof.\n"
"\n"
"## The challenge\n"
"\n"
"Consider a function from §0 to §1. The domain is a\n"
"product type with §2 elements. The codomain has §3 elements.\n"
"Since §4, by pigeonhole there must be a collision: two distinct\n"
"inputs that map to the same output.\n"
"\n"
"## What you need\n"
"\n"
"1. §5 to set up pigeonhole.\n"
"2. §6 to decompose the product type cardinality.\n"
"3. §7 to evaluate the cardinalities.\n"
"4. Arithmetic (§8) to close §9.\n"
"\n"
"This integrates the counting computation from Level 1 with the\n"
"pigeonhole application from Level 2."
