msgid "When you coerce a list to a multiset with §0, the **cardinality is preserved**:\n"
"§1 for any list §2. This is a **definitional equality**,\n"
"which is why §3 works -- Lean does not need a lemma to verify it, just unfolding.\n"
"\n"
"The distinction between definitional equality (provable by §4) and propositional\n"
"equality (requiring §5 or other tactics) is fundamental in Lean. Here, the fact\n"
"that §6 is defined in terms of §7 makes this definitional.\n"
"\n"
