#: Game.Levels.FinsetTransformations.L08_Boss
msgid "# Boss: Combining filter and image\n"
"\n"
"Time to integrate everything from this world. You will prove a result\n"
"that chains §0 and §1 together and requires unpacking both.\n"
"\n"
"## The statement\n"
"\n"
