"- **Part A**: Introduce §8 and the hypothesis §9, unpack using\n"
"  §10 and §11, then build the target membership.\n"
"- **Part B**: Apply §12 directly.\n"
"\n"
"This boss integrates membership reasoning AND cardinality reasoning."
