#: Game.Levels.ListBasics.L03_ListMem
msgid "# Proving membership symbolically\n"
"\n"
"Given a list §0 and an element §1, the proposition §2 asserts that\n"
"§3 appears somewhere in §4. For **concrete** lists like §5, you\n"
"could verify membership with §6. But in this level, you will prove\n"
"membership **symbolically** -- for an arbitrary list.\n"
"\n"
"## How membership unfolds\n"
"\n"
"The membership relation for lists is defined recursively:\n"
"- §7 is §8 (nothing is in the empty list)\n"
"- §9 is §10 (either §11 is the head, or §12 is in the tail)\n"
"\n"
"The key rewriting lemma is §13:\n"
"§14\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Prove that for any list §15, the element §16 is in §17.\n"
"\n"
"Since §18 is the head of §19, you know §20 holds.\n"
"You need to show §21 -- and the left disjunct is true.\n"
"\n"
"**Strategy**:\n"
"1. Use §22 to unfold the membership\n"
"2. Use §23 to choose the left disjunct\n"
"3. Close with §24"
