msgid "# Case-splitting on a membership hypothesis\n"
"\n"
"So far you have proved concrete membership facts: specific numbers in\n"
"specific finsets. But what about **symbolic** membership? When you have\n"
"a hypothesis §0 where §1 is a *variable*, you\n"
"cannot just use §2 -- you need to reason about what §3 could be.\n"
"\n"
"## Rewriting hypotheses with §4\n"
"\n"
"You already know §5 rewrites the **goal**. But\n"
"you can also rewrite a **hypothesis**:\n"
"\n"
"§6\n"
"\n"
"This transforms §7 into §8.\n"
"\n"
"## Case-splitting with §9\n"
"\n"
"Once §10 is a disjunction §11, you can case-split:\n"
"\n"
"§12\n"
"\n"
"This creates two goals:\n"
"- In the first, §13 substitutes §14 for §15 everywhere. The variable\n"
"  §16 disappears and is replaced by §17.\n"
"- In the second, §18 gives you the membership in the\n"
"  smaller finset.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
