msgid "# Proving subset relations\n"
"\n"
"A finset §0 is a **subset** of §1, written §2, when every\n"
"element of §3 is also an element of §4:\n"
"\n"
"§5\n"
"\n"
"In practice, §6 **unfolds** to §7. So to prove\n"
"a subset relation, you introduce an element and a membership hypothesis,\n"
"then show the element belongs to the larger finset.\n"
"\n"
"## Notation\n"
"\n"
"The symbol §8 is typed §9 or §10.\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Prove that §11 for arbitrary finsets §12 and §13. This says\n"
"that every finset is a subset of its union with any other finset.\n"
"\n"
"**Strategy**: Introduce §14 and §15, then show §16\n"
"by rewriting with §17 and choosing the left branch."
msgstr ""

