"## The three swap evaluation rules\n"
"\n"
"When evaluating §0, there are three cases:\n"
"\n"
"| Case | Lemma | Result |\n"
"|------|-------|--------|\n"
"| §1 | §2 | §3 |\n"
"| §4 | §5 | §6 |\n"
"| §7 and §8 | §9 | §10 |\n"
"\n"
