#: Game.Levels.Factorials.L06_CountingPerms
msgid "# Factorials count permutations\n"
"\n"
"A **permutation** of a set is a bijection from the set to itself —\n"
"a rearrangement of its elements. The number of permutations of an\n"
"§0-element set is §1.\n"
"\n"
"## In Lean\n"
"\n"
"Lean represents permutations of a type §2 as §3,\n"
"which is the type of bijections from §4 to §5. Mathlib provides:\n"
"\n"
"§6\n"
"\n"
"This says: the number of permutations of §7 equals\n"
"§8.\n"
"\n"
"For §9, we also need:\n"
"\n"
"§10\n"
"\n"
"## Your task\n"
"\n"
"Prove that the number of permutations of §11 (a 3-element set)\n"
"is 6.\n"
"\n"
"## Strategy\n"
"\n"
