"\n"
"## Two directions of factorial_succ\n"
"\n"
"- **Breaking down**: §1 (used in L01 for computation)\n"
"- **Building up**: §2 (used here for algebraic reasoning)\n"
"\n"
"Both directions use the same lemma §3; the only\n"
"difference is whether you read it left-to-right or right-to-left.\n"
"\n"
"## What comes next\n"
"\n"
