"\n"
"The §1 tactic is specialized for **numeric computations**. It can\n"
"evaluate arithmetic expressions, verify equalities and inequalities\n"
"involving concrete numbers, and simplify numeric goals.\n"
"\n"
"## How §2 differs from §3\n"
"\n"
"- §4 works with **linear** arithmetic over natural numbers and\n"
